        <updateDate>2007-08-09T14:42:59Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Directs the Secretary of Transportation, in providing assistance for projects to eliminate hazards of railway-highway crossings, to give priority consideration to emergency grade crossing safety improvements at railroad grade crossings where there have been multiple serious collisions.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
